      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "There are countless bloggers who’d hate to be professional writers.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Which is why—when they’re not writing—they so often choose to make a living doing something else.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Before she started",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Brain Pickings",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ", Maria Popova worked in advertising.",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Seth Godin",
          "marks": [
            "link-1"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "did marketing.",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Brett Mckay",
          "marks": [
            "link-2"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "was set to be a lawyer.",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Tim Urban",
          "marks": [
            "link-3"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "did test-prep. And",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Peter Adeney",
          "marks": [
            "link-4"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "was a software engineer.",
          "marks": []
        }
